name: Lara and the Jade Skull
summary: Once more, Lara finds herself in the depths of a lush jungle, exploring an ancient temple. Unfortunately for the experienced raider however, she isn’t alone. Two muscular men stand behind her, grinning with anticipation. Lara has two choices – she can either fight or choose to employ every tool at her disposal. Using her assets to her advantage, the lithe brunette seduces and fucks her pursuants. She uses all of her holes strategically to ensure that she reaches her objective. And when she’s done with them, the men have no choice but to let her go with the ultimate prize. The Jade Skull is hers for the taking.
